    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some clear coat fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It's a reliable workhorse that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a showroom-quality model.",
