    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you're getting a great vehicle that still looks and feels fantastic. Come give it a new home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
