    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2003 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-strung S54B32 atmospheric inline-six. This unit features a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Key preventative maintenance is documented: the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system overhauled to ensure variable valve timing precision. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, while the individual throttle bodies provide immediate throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Presented in good condition, this M3 balances cosmetic patina with uncompromising mechanical integrity, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated driver.",
